OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA band of
OL,6,Frain, heavy at times, especially over
OL,7,Fwestern hills, will move quickly
OL,8,Feastwards across all areas this
OL,9,Fevening. This clearing during the
OL,10,Fearly hours of Wednesday morning,
OL,11,Fafter which it will become dry with
OL,12,Fsome clear spells. Windy.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FA breezy day, although it
OL,15,Fshould be largely dry with bright or
OL,16,Fsunny spells. Chance of a few showers
OL,17,Freaching western parts later in the
OL,18,Fday. Staying mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
